des:
Ask for KBO Facts, and learn about KBO League.

KBO Facts provides fun the international sports fans can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter about KBO league.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch KBO Facts" or "Alexa, open KBO Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
